%N A015959 Inverse of 1950th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015959 Periodic with period length 1950. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015959 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015959/b015959.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015959 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1950.
